
FUNCTION ScreenCapture GLOBAL
    UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: Browser
    UIAutomation.ResizeWindow.ResizeByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: Browser Width: width Height: height

    IF ButtonPressed = $'''Cancel''' THEN
        EXIT FUNCTION
    END
    WAIT 1
    LABEL PrintWebPage
    Workstation.GetDefaultPrinter PrinterName=> PrinterName
    Workstation.SetDefaultPrinter PrinterName: $'''Microsoft Print to PDF'''
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: Browser TextToSend: $'''{Control}{Shift}({P})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 1
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindowContent.WindowToContainElement Element: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Window \'印刷\''])
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByControl Control: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Window \'印刷\''] TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({L}){Alt}({P})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 500 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 1
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpen Window: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Window \'印刷結果を名前を付けて保存\''] FocusWindow: True)
    UIAutomation.PopulateTextField TextField: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Edit \'ファイル名:\''] Text: $'''%SelectedFolder%\\%title%_%layout%_print.pdf''' Mode: UIAutomation.PopulateTextMode.Replace ClickType: UIAutomation.PopulateMouseClickType.SingleClick
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByControl Control: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Window \'印刷結果を名前を付けて保存\''] TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({S})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 1
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindowContent.WindowToNotContainElement Element: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Window \'印刷結果を名前を付けて保存の確認\''])
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindowContent.WindowToNotContainElement Element: appmask['Pane \'Google Chrome\'']['Window \'印刷結果を名前を付けて保存\''])
    Workstation.SetDefaultPrinter PrinterName: PrinterName
    LABEL CaptureWebPage
    Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessage Title: $'''レイアウト''' Message: $'''画面キャプチャにあたって、画面下部の描画のためにスクロールが必要であれば実施してください''' Icon: Display.Icon.Information Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: True ButtonPressed=> ButtonPressed
    WAIT 1
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: Browser TextToSend: $'''{F12}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 3
    UIAutomation.GetWindow.GetUseTimeout Control: appmask['Pane \'DevTools\''] BringWindowToFront: True Timeout: 5 WindowInstance=> AutomationWindow
    UIAutomation.SetWindowState.SetStateByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: AutomationWindow State: UIAutomation.WindowState.Restored
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: AutomationWindow TextToSend: $'''{Control}{Shift}({P})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 1
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: AutomationWindow TextToSend: $'''full{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT 3
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindowContent.WindowToContainElement Element: appmask['Pane \'DevTools\'']['Window \'名前を付けて保存\''])
    UIAutomation.PopulateTextField TextField: appmask['Pane \'DevTools\'']['Edit \'ファイル名:\''] Text: $'''%SelectedFolder%\\%title%_%layout%.png''' Mode: UIAutomation.PopulateTextMode.Replace ClickType: UIAutomation.PopulateMouseClickType.SingleClick
    WAIT 1
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByControl Control: appmask['Pane \'DevTools\'']['Window \'名前を付けて保存\''] TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({S})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 1
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindowContent.WindowToNotContainElement Element: appmask['Pane \'DevTools\'']['Window \'名前を付けて保存の確認\''])
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindowContent.WindowToNotContainElement Element: appmask['Pane \'DevTools\'']['Window \'名前を付けて保存\''])
    WAIT 1
    UIAutomation.CloseWindow.CloseByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: AutomationWindow
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: Browser TextToSend: $'''{Escape}{Home}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
END FUNCTION
